   "source": [
    "##### \n",
    "$$dS_t = rS_t\\,dt + \\sqrt{v_t}\\,S_t\\,dW_t^{(1)}$$\n",
    "$$dv_t = \\kappa(\\theta - v_t)\\,dt + \\xi\\sqrt{v_t}\\,dW_t^{(2)}$$\n",
    "$$dW_t^{(1)}\\,dW_t^{(2)} = \\rho\\,dt$$"
